Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: SIMPLY SPECTACULAR! One of a kind bi-level condo in the heart of City Point, just steps to beach & Castle Island. Amazing floor plan offers open living/kitchen/dining area w/gas FP, formal LR, 4th BR & 1/2 bath. Recently remodeled kitchen. The upper level has 2 add'l BR's PLUS a massive master BR suite w/2nd gas FP and recently remodeled bathroom. Every amenity offered inlc. w/hw fls thru, custom kitchen & baths, 2 huge decks, one w/water views & GARAGE parking. Great for entertaining, not enough words to describe this must see property!!
